NewInfo-&gt;<a href="/docs/api/structs/llvm/amdgpu/mimginfo/#a5779a9eb60048bf4ff930445561e64d1">Opcode</a> : -1;</span></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00291" /><CodeLine lineNumber="291"><span class="doxyHighlight">&#125;</span></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00292" /><CodeLine lineNumber="292"></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00293" /><CodeLine lineNumber="293" lineLink="/docs/api/namespaces/llvm/amdgpu/#a9af58a5d20f2215a00b675f34db92771"><span class="doxyHighlightKeywordType">unsigned</span><span class="doxyHighlight"> <a href="/docs/api/namespaces/llvm/amdgpu/#a9af58a5d20f2215a00b675f34db92771">getAddrSizeMIMGOp</a>(</span><span class="doxyHighlightKeyword">const</span><span class="doxyHighlight"> <a href="/docs/api/structs/llvm/amdgpu/mimgbaseopcodeinfo">MIMGBaseOpcodeInfo</a> &#42;BaseOpcode,</span></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00294" /><CodeLine lineNumber="294"><span class="doxyHighlight">                           </span><span class="doxyHighlightKeyword">const</span><span class="doxyHighlight"> <a href="/docs/api/structs/llvm/amdgpu/mimgdiminfo">MIMGDimInfo</a> &#42;Dim, </span><span class="doxyHighlightKeywordType">bool</span><span class="doxyHighlight"> IsA16,</span></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00295" /><CodeLine lineNumber="295"><span class="doxyHighlight">                           </span><span class="doxyHighlightKeywordType">bool</span><span class="doxyHighlight"> IsG16Supported) &#123;</span></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00296" /><CodeLine lineNumber="296"><span class="doxyHighlight">  </span><span class="doxyHighlightKeywordType">unsigned</span><span class="doxyHighlight"> AddrWords = BaseOpcode-&gt;<a href="/docs/api/structs/llvm/amdgpu/mimgbaseopcodeinfo/#aed9d22e06865e4b6c99b16e9731dd405">NumExtraArgs</a>;</span></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00297" /><CodeLine lineNumber="297"><span class="doxyHighlight">  </span><span class="doxyHighlightKeywordType">unsigned</span><span class="doxyHighlight"> AddrComponents = (BaseOpcode-&gt;<a href="/docs/api/structs/llvm/amdgpu/mimgbaseopcodeinfo/#a70ffab1206752dada12358c20e0cbfb5">Coordinates</a> ? Dim-&gt;<a href="/docs/api/structs/llvm/amdgpu/mimgdiminfo/#a116a4083ecfd14f2d8c4e79d8bf9944a">NumCoords</a> : 0) +</span></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00298" /><CodeLine lineNumber="298"><span class="doxyHighlight">                            (BaseOpcode-&gt;<a href="/docs/api/structs/llvm/amdgpu/mimgbaseopcodeinfo/#a6b7b54de13fab37e46a6aee073ff101f">LodOrClampOrMip</a> ? 1 : 0);</span></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00299" /><CodeLine lineNumber="299"><span class="doxyHighlight">  </span><span class="doxyHighlightKeywordFlow">if</span><span class="doxyHighlight"> (IsA16)</span></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00300" /><CodeLine lineNumber="300"><span class="doxyHighlight">    AddrWords += <a href="/docs/api/namespaces/llvm/#a9dda4472ee0b7ea92ab49eedf6e13d50">divideCeil</a>(AddrComponents, 2);</span></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00301" /><CodeLine lineNumber="301"><span class="doxyHighlight">  </span><span class="doxyHighlightKeywordFlow">else</span></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00302" /><CodeLine lineNumber="302"><span class="doxyHighlight">    AddrWords += AddrComponents;</span></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00303" /><CodeLine lineNumber="303"></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00304" /><CodeLine lineNumber="304"><span class="doxyHighlight">  </span><span class="doxyHighlightComment">// Note: For subtargets that support A16 but not G16, enabling A16 also</span></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00305" /><CodeLine lineNumber="305"><span class="doxyHighlight">  </span><span class="doxyHighlightComment">// enables 16 bit gradients.</span></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00306" /><CodeLine lineNumber="306"><span class="doxyHighlight">  </span><span class="doxyHighlightComment">// For subtargets that support A16 (operand) and G16 (done with a different</span></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00307" /><CodeLine lineNumber="307"><span class="doxyHighlight">  </span><span class="doxyHighlightComment">// instruction encoding), they are independent.</span></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00308" /><CodeLine lineNumber="308"></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00309" /><CodeLine lineNumber="309"><span class="doxyHighlight">  </span><span class="doxyHighlightKeywordFlow">if</span><span class="doxyHighlight"> (BaseOpcode-&gt;<a href="/docs/api/structs/llvm/amdgpu/mimgbaseopcodeinfo/#a0adbb6ce25f3ffd10c57280e27cc2cd2">Gradients</a>) &#123;</span></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00310" /><CodeLine lineNumber="310"><span class="doxyHighlight">    </span><span class="doxyHighlightKeywordFlow">if</span><span class="doxyHighlight"> ((IsA16 &amp;&amp; !IsG16Supported) || BaseOpcode-&gt;<a href="/docs/api/structs/llvm/amdgpu/mimgbaseopcodeinfo/#a28a103d56d5fd5dd97634d79c774e677">G16</a>)</span></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00311" /><CodeLine lineNumber="311"><span class="doxyHighlight">      </span><span class="doxyHighlightComment">// There are two gradients per coordinate, we pack them separately.</span></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00312" /><CodeLine lineNumber="312"><span class="doxyHighlight">      </span><span class="doxyHighlightComment">// For the 3d case,</span></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00313" /><CodeLine lineNumber="313"><span class="doxyHighlight">      </span><span class="doxyHighlightComment">// we get (dy/du, dx/du) (-, dz/du) (dy/dv, dx/dv) (-, dz/dv)</span></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00314" /><CodeLine lineNumber="314"><span class="doxyHighlight">      AddrWords += <a href="/docs/api/namespaces/llvm/#ab102f0f12dd38aeea5906b1d80c792ff">alignTo&lt;2&gt;</a>(Dim-&gt;<a href="/docs/api/structs/llvm/amdgpu/mimgdiminfo/#a500a440f5ad12b5a95e9bf4c5bfc9401">NumGradients</a> / 2);</span></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00315" /><CodeLine lineNumber="315"><span class="doxyHighlight">    </span><span class="doxyHighlightKeywordFlow">else</span></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00316" /><CodeLine lineNumber="316"><span class="doxyHighlight">      AddrWords += Dim-&gt;<a href="/docs/api/structs/llvm/amdgpu/mimgdiminfo/#a500a440f5ad12b5a95e9bf4c5bfc9401">NumGradients</a>;</span></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00317" /><CodeLine lineNumber="317"><span class="doxyHighlight">  &#125;</span></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00318" /><CodeLine lineNumber="318"><span class="doxyHighlight">  </span><span class="doxyHighlightKeywordFlow">return</span><span class="doxyHighlight"> AddrWords;</span></CodeLine>
